actual.config:
! Command: show running-config
! device: leaf3 (vEOS, EOS-4.22.3M)
!
! boot system flash:/.boot-image.swi
!
daemon AosEosProxySdkAgent
   exec /usr/bin/AosEosProxySdkAgent 
   no shutdown
!
ip dhcp relay information option
ip dhcp relay always-on
!
service interface inactive expose
!
transceiver qsfp default-mode 4x10G
!
service routing protocols model multi-agent
!
hostname leaf3
!
spanning-tree mode rapid-pvst
spanning-tree vlan 1-4094 priority 8192
!
aaa authorization exec default local
!
aaa root secret sha512 $6$D5R.dcATWBnoe.52$4M4KZL9pYK57rSlV2A2O4kEWhKg5uuYtjfV6ChPGQdvYSLhP/u0tsVjVkd2ieVuJOdE7o7IMBoQh/ptrV9ARp.
aaa authentication policy local allow-nopassword-remote-login
!
username admin privilege 15 role network-admin secret sha512 $6$biGVjH1AbZdtkQO9$12QiFTl18jEztXcOHBcGsoxD/2N0SED3wkxCKpbBCpY/xHPkcVhv1/MVj9C2Vbk9VNVtJqii7vAGeU6OqHtjS/
!
vlan 31
   name vlan_31_leaf3_v4
!
vlan 100
   name blue_vxlan_100_v4
!
vlan 101
   name default_vxlan_101_v4
!
vlan 102
   name red_vxlan_102_v4
!
vlan 121
   name blue_121_leaf3_v4
!
vlan 123
   name default_123_leaf3_v4
!
vlan 125
   name red_125_leaf3_v4
!
vlan 200
   name VRF_red
!
vlan 201
   name VRF_blue
!
vrf definition blue
!
vrf definition management
   rd 100:100
!
vrf definition red
!
interface Ethernet1
   description facing_spine1:swp1
   no switchport
   ip address 172.16.0.5/31
!
interface Ethernet2
   description facing_spine2:swp1
   no switchport
   ip address 172.16.0.11/31
!
interface Ethernet3
   description to.leaf3-server1
   switchport trunk native vlan 31
   switchport trunk allowed vlan 31,100-102,121,123,125
   switchport mode trunk
!
interface Ethernet4
   no switchport
!
interface Ethernet5
   no switchport
!
interface Ethernet6
   no switchport
!
interface Ethernet7
   no switchport
!
interface Loopback0
   ip address 10.0.0.4/32
!
interface Loopback1
   ip address 10.0.0.12/32
   ip address 10.0.0.11/32 secondary
!
interface Loopback2
   description Loopback for VRF red
   vrf forwarding red
   ip address 10.0.0.7/32
!
interface Loopback3
   description Loopback for VRF blue
   vrf forwarding blue
   ip address 10.0.0.10/32
!
interface Management1
   vrf forwarding management
   ip address 172.20.199.14/24
!
interface Vlan31
   description vlan_31_leaf3_v4
   ip address 192.168.31.2/24
   ip helper-address 198.51.100.2
   ip dhcp relay information option circuit-id x-1234
!
interface Vlan100
   description blue_vxlan_100_v4
   vrf forwarding blue
   ip helper-address 198.51.100.2 source-interface Loopback3
   ip dhcp relay information option circuit-id x-1234
   ip address virtual 192.168.100.1/24
!
interface Vlan101
   description default_vxlan_101_v4
   ip helper-address 198.51.100.2
   ip dhcp relay information option circuit-id x-1234
   ip address virtual 192.168.101.1/24
!
interface Vlan102
   description red_vxlan_102_v4
   vrf forwarding red
   ip helper-address 198.51.100.2 source-interface Loopback2
   ip dhcp relay information option circuit-id x-1234
   ip address virtual 192.168.102.1/24
!
interface Vlan121
   description blue_121_leaf3_v4
   vrf forwarding blue
   ip helper-address 198.51.100.2 source-interface Loopback3
   ip dhcp relay information option circuit-id x-1234
   ip address virtual 192.168.121.1/24
!
interface Vlan123
   description default_123_leaf3_v4
   ip helper-address 198.51.100.2
   ip dhcp relay information option circuit-id x-1234
   ip address virtual 192.168.123.1/24
!
interface Vlan125
   description red_125_leaf3_v4
   vrf forwarding red
   ip helper-address 198.51.100.2 source-interface Loopback2
   ip dhcp relay information option circuit-id x-1234
   ip address virtual 192.168.125.1/24
!
interface Vxlan1
   vxlan source-interface Loopback1
   vxlan udp-port 4789
   vxlan vlan 100 vni 10000
   vxlan vlan 101 vni 10001
   vxlan vlan 102 vni 10002
   vxlan vlan 121 vni 25001
   vxlan vlan 125 vni 25005
   vxlan vrf blue vni 20002
   vxlan vrf red vni 20001
!
ip virtual-router mac-address 00:1c:73:00:00:01
!
ip route vrf management 0.0.0.0/0 172.20.199.1
!
ip routing
ip routing vrf blue
ip routing vrf management
ip routing vrf red
!
ip as-path access-list MyASN permit ^$ any
ip prefix-list AllPodNetworks seq 5 permit 0.0.0.0/0 le 32
!
route-map AdvLocal permit 10
   match as-path MyASN
!
route-map AllPodNetworks permit 10
   match ip address prefix-list AllPodNetworks
!
router bgp 64516
   router-id 10.0.0.4
   no bgp default ipv4-unicast
   maximum-paths 32
   neighbor l3clos-l peer-group
   neighbor l3clos-l timers 1 3
   neighbor l3clos-l maximum-routes 0 warning-limit 90 percent
   neighbor l3clos-l-evpn peer-group
   neighbor l3clos-l-evpn update-source Loopback0
   neighbor l3clos-l-evpn allowas-in 1
   neighbor l3clos-l-evpn ebgp-multihop 2
   neighbor l3clos-l-evpn timers 1 3
   neighbor l3clos-l-evpn send-community extended
   neighbor l3clos-l-evpn maximum-routes 0 warning-limit 90 percent
   neighbor 10.0.0.0 peer-group l3clos-l-evpn
   neighbor 10.0.0.0 remote-as 64512
   neighbor 10.0.0.0 description facing_spine1-evpn-overlay
   neighbor 10.0.0.1 peer-group l3clos-l-evpn
   neighbor 10.0.0.1 remote-as 64513
   neighbor 10.0.0.1 description facing_spine2-evpn-overlay
   neighbor 172.16.0.4 peer-group l3clos-l
   neighbor 172.16.0.4 remote-as 64512
   neighbor 172.16.0.4 description facing_spine1
   neighbor 172.16.0.10 peer-group l3clos-l
   neighbor 172.16.0.10 remote-as 64513
   neighbor 172.16.0.10 description facing_spine2
   redistribute connected route-map AllPodNetworks
   !
   vlan 100
      rd 10.0.0.4:100
      route-target both 10000:1
      redistribute learned
   !
   vlan 101
      rd 10.0.0.4:101
      route-target both 10001:1
      redistribute learned
   !
   vlan 102
      rd 10.0.0.4:102
      route-target both 10002:1
      redistribute learned
   !
   vlan 121
      rd 10.0.0.4:121
      route-target both 25001:1
      redistribute learned
   !
   vlan 125
      rd 10.0.0.4:125
      route-target both 25005:1
      redistribute learned
   !
   vlan 200
      rd 10.0.0.4:200
      route-target both 20001:1
      redistribute learned
   !
   vlan 201
      rd 10.0.0.4:201
      route-target both 20002:1
      redistribute learned
   !
   address-family evpn
      neighbor 10.0.0.0 activate
      neighbor 10.0.0.1 activate
   !
   address-family ipv4
      neighbor l3clos-l route-map AdvLocal out
      neighbor 172.16.0.4 activate
      neighbor 172.16.0.10 activate
   !
   vrf blue
      rd 10.0.0.4:201
      bgp log-neighbor-changes
      redistribute connected route-map AllPodNetworks
      !
      address-family ipv4
         route-target import 20002:1
         route-target export 20002:1
   !
   vrf red
      rd 10.0.0.4:200
      bgp log-neighbor-changes
      redistribute connected route-map AllPodNetworks
      !
      address-family ipv4
         route-target import 20001:1
         route-target export 20001:1
!
management api http-commands
   protocol http
   protocol unix-socket
   no shutdown
   !
   vrf management
      no shutdown
!
end
